WEBVTT

00:03.864 --> 00:05.965
How's your mom
holding up?

00:05.967 --> 00:09.135
She's doing okay, but we just
lost another nurse.

00:09.137 --> 00:10.370
How many is that now?

00:10.372 --> 00:12.038
Two, and I know what
you're thinking--

00:12.040 --> 00:14.207
she's eating them.

00:16.277 --> 00:18.544
She's just so impossible,
they keep quitting.

00:18.546 --> 00:20.146
So, who's
watching her now?

00:20.148 --> 00:23.750
A bowl full of M&M's with
a few Ambien tossed in.

00:23.752 --> 00:25.318
What up, guys?

00:25.320 --> 00:26.586
Hello. - Hey.  -Hello.

00:26.588 --> 00:28.621
Okay.

00:28.623 --> 00:30.123
Well, now that
everyone's here,

00:30.125 --> 00:32.759
Penny and I have
some big news.

00:33.360 --> 00:34.560
We're engaged!

00:41.035 --> 00:43.236
And I thought me having sex with
Emily was gonna be the big news.

00:47.108 --> 00:48.775
Hey! Hey!

00:49.943 --> 00:51.978
What the hell!

00:51.980 --> 00:53.780
You guys propose all the time.

00:53.782 --> 00:56.082
This never happens.

00:56.084 --> 00:57.550
You're right!

01:00.155 --> 01:03.790
♪ Our whole universe
was in a hot, dense state ♪

01:03.792 --> 01:07.126
♪ Then nearly 14 billion years
ago expansion started... Wait! ♪

01:07.128 --> 01:08.728
♪ The Earth began to cool

01:08.730 --> 01:11.297
♪ The autotrophs began to drool,
Neanderthals developed tools ♪

01:11.299 --> 01:13.966
♪ We built the Wall
♪ <i>We built the pyramids</i> ♪

01:13.968 --> 01:16.636
♪ Math, Science, History,
unraveling the mystery ♪

01:16.638 --> 01:18.504
♪ That all started
with a big bang ♪

01:18.506 --> 01:20.506
♪ <i>Bang!</i> ♪

01:20.536 --> 01:24.536
